Steps
1.Clone
   git clone https://github.com/jnkssm/Marine_port_public.git
2.Intsall requirement.txt
  pip install -r [file path]requirements.txt
3.Create environmrnt
  Windows: python -m venv mr_port_simulation
  macOS/Linux: python3 -m venv mr_port_simulation
4.Activating Your Custom Environment
  Windows: .\mr_port_simulation\Scripts\Activate.ps1
  macOS/Linux: source mr_port_simulation/bin/activate
5.Load Ollama

6.Install Ollama
   Window: pip install ollama
7.Close and reopen VS Code
8.Pull model (Large file models) - both Win and Mac
   ollama pull llama2
   ollama pull llama3
9.Check model list
   ollama list


